Snap your best nudes 🤩with our new #BOMBPOSSE Mega Mix & Match Eyeshadow palette! This snappable palette lets you play with a range of looks and pops on all skin tones. 🙌🏼🙌🏽🙌🏾 Get a subtle everyday look or an extra AF show-stopping glam with your fave #GLOSSBOMB inspired shades, #FENTYGLOW, FU$$Y, and #HOTCHOCOLIT! ✨

Mark your calendars for this drop on September 9th at fentybeauty.com, @sephora, @harveynichols, @bootsuk and #SephorainJCP.
